9:
Thank you for all your help today,
Nao. I hope it wasn't too much work...
15:
Not at all! Marina's taking a break
from work right now, so I've got
plenty of free time!
19:
Still... You came here without your
brother's permission, didn't you?
22:
If you just wait here for a moment, I'll
find you an escort to accompany
you home...
29:
Ugh, why's everyone so
overprotective lately... I'm a PIRATE
now, for goodness' sake.
40: Don't worry, I've got your back!
43:
Aw jeez, reinforcements? Whatever, I
can still—
51:
Chika! I told you to stop coming
here!
55: Whoa! A wild bad boy appeared!
59:
That hair... You related to that
Nagihara kid or something?
72:
No, I don't wanna! Why are you
being like this, Toto?!
74:
I already told you. A kid without
powers isn't cut out for this way of
life.
80:
U-um... I know this isn't my business,
but...
83:
You two are siblings, right? But you
just told her to "go home." So if the
place you're staying is too
dangerous...
87: Why not just... go home with her?
91: I'm the former leader of Aegis.
94:
Naturally, that comes with its fair
share of grudges. If word got out
Chika's my sister, I can think of more
than a few scumbags who would
take advantage of that.
96:
So living together's out of the
question.
106:
I heard your brother's group has
been taking in former Aegis
members. Is that true?
110:
...Yeah. Plus, anyone living in
Palpebra has Zekhel and the others
behind them. Mr. Takamori's working
hard to make Shibuya a better
place too.
114:
Then that settles it. Chika, you're
going with her.
117:
B-but what about you, Toto? We
should go together!
119:
I can't. Scum like me belongs on the
streets.
122:
So make sure you don't end up like
me. Goodbye, Chika.
127: Okay, well, see you later... NOT!
132:
Are all brothers this STUPID?!
Seriously, Chika! Don't they just piss
you off?
135:
Y-yeah! Why do I gotta listen to
what you have to say!
141:
First Kazu dies, and now you're
leaving me too?! That means I'll be
all alone!
143:
Why would you do something so
MEAN?!
151:
In that case... What if I told you
about the safest place in the
world—no, multiple worlds?!
162:
Aaand that's the story! Do the thing,
Stella!
166:
All right. Welcome to Starview
Village, Chika and Tohru.
175:
What? Stella already welcomed
them, so that's that, right?
179:
Well, yeah... And it's not like I'm
opposed or anything, but...
183: Are you really okay with this, Tohru?
188:
...As long as my sister's safe, I don't
care where we are. Even if it does
end up biting me in the ass later.
191:
So, what do I gotta do in return?
Anybody you need taken care of?
199: Although we do have ONE condition.
203:
Make sure you write your name on
anything you put in the fridge.
211:
Nope. But make sure you follow that
rule.
215: Come on, I'll give you the grand tour!
225:
Hoo boy... Sho's in for the shock of
his life...
228: Eh. I'm sure it'll be fine.
